      "type": "p",
      "text": "False Appearance. While the mephit remains motionless, it is indistinguishable from an ordinary shard of ice."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Innate Spellcasting (1/Day). The mephit can innately cast fog cloud , requiring no material components. Its innate spellcasting ability is Charisma."
    },
