      "text": "Actions"
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Claws. Melee Weapon Attack: +3 to hit, reach 5 ft., one creature. Hit: 3 (1d4 + 1) slashing damage plus 2 (1d4) cold damage."
    },
    {
      "type": "p",
      "text": "Frost Breath (Recharge 6). The mephit exhales a 15-- foot cone of cold air. Each creature in that area must succeed on a DC 10 Dexterity saving throw, taking 5"
